@startuml
title MediZano - Tiempo de inventario
robust "Movimiento" as Mov
robust "Lote" as Lote
robust "Stock" as Stock
robust "Alerta" as Alerta
@0
Mov is Pendiente
Lote is Disponible
Stock is Normal
Alerta is Inactiva
@5
Mov is RegistrandoSalida
Stock is Actualizando
@10
Mov is Confirmado
Stock is Bajo
Alerta is Evaluando
@15
Alerta is Notificada
@20
Mov is RegistrandoEntrada
Stock is Normal
Alerta is Cerrada
@enduml
